## üìã TEMPLATE SECTIONS EXPLAINED

### **Meta Tags Section**
```html
<title>[PRIMARY KEYWORD]: [SPECIFIC BENEFIT] (2025) | ContentScale</title>
```
AI must: Replace with actual title, include year, keep under 60 chars

### **Schema Markup Section**
```json
"headline": "[Article title - max 110 characters]"
```
AI must: Fill ALL schema fields, use actual dates, validate after

### **H1 Title**
```html
<h1>[PRIMARY KEYWORD]: [SPECIFIC BENEFIT/OUTCOME] (2025)</h1>
```
AI must: Include keyword, benefit, year (2025)

### **Introduction (First 150 Words)**
```html
<p class="text-xl">
  [SENTENCE 1: PRIMARY KEYWORD definition]
  [SENTENCE 2: Proof point]
  [etc...]
</p>
```
AI must: Follow exact structure, include all 8 sentences

### **Main Content Sections**
```html
<h2 id="section1">What is [Primary Keyword]?</h2>
```
AI must: Create 8-12 H2 sections minimum, each with substantial content

### **FAQ Section**
```html
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/FAQPage">
```
AI must: Add 10-15 questions with proper schema markup

