## üéØ EXAMPLE PROMPT TO AI

```
Write a perfect 100/100 SEO article using these two files:

1. Follow the "100/100 ContentScale Prompt" for all requirements
2. Use "PERFECT-100-100-ARTICLE-TEMPLATE.html" for structure

TOPIC: "GRAAF Framework Complete Guide"
